snippet.title: Spore Galactic Adventures Launch Trailer - The Space Captain
snippet.description:
Take a look at the first expansion pack to Spore. See our Space Captain go from zero to Galactic Hero as he equips cool new accessories and conquers dangerous new missions! Check out the new Adventure Creator complete with all the tools youll need to create infinite adventures. Where will your adventures take your captain?

Spore Galactic Adventures - beaming down June 23

www.spore.com
